{
  "stem": "25591.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Later on, she decided that the Holocaust Museum in Washington be placed on Raoul Wallenberg Place, so we went through the process of renaming that street.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She did it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then, not long ago she succeeded in having a bust of Raoul Wallenberg placed in the capital, which was a tremendous achievement.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Hundreds of people whose lives Raoul saved flew in from Australia, New Zealand, Europe, Canada, over the United States, Hungary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then she worked on a Raoul Wallenberg stamp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Soon in every post office, you'll be able to buy Raoul Wallenberg stamp, which is her doing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She has given much of her life to it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she has been my inspiration in the work of human rights.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very much so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very much so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] You don't need to be a rocket scientist to realize how much power there is in the political arena.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A Hitler, a Stalin, a Saddam Hussein, a Gaddafi-- or conversely for good.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Great political leaders can-- can achieve wonderful things and bad political leaders can create a nightmare.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And since money was never very important to me, I felt I wanted to be in public service.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So for 33 years I was in university teaching, which is a form of public service.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And for the last 16, I've been in Congress, which is another form of public service.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I-- I wouldn't trade a minute of these 49 years for anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's not my achievements.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the first place, Annette and I have worked as a team on every project.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Secondly, when you are in government in a democratic society, you realize that you don't achieve anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You can only get anyplace by motivating your colleagues and lots of other people to-- to work with you.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
